/// <br>
/// The above exploits <a class="rosetta__link--wiki" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Call-by-name#Call_by_name" title="wp: Call-by-name#Call_by_name">call by name</a> to produce the correct answer (5.187...). It depends on the assumption that an expression passed as an actual parameter to a procedure would be re-evaluated in the caller's context every time the corresponding formal parameter's value was required. If the last parameter to <span class="rosetta__text--italic">sum</span> had been passed by value, and assuming the initial value of <span class="rosetta__text--italic">i</span> were 1, the result would have been 100 &times; 1/1 = 100.
